# /opt/stacks/cloud/.env.example — placeholder file for IdP mode.
#
# Before SSO migration this file held SAGAN_PW_HASH / MARCUS_PW_HASH
# (argon2 digests of per-user copyparty passwords). With Authelia in
# the path, identity comes from Remote-User / Remote-Groups headers
# (see conf/copyparty.conf) and copyparty no longer needs local
# password material.
#
# Kept committed as a stub so future operators know an .env was once
# expected; copy to /opt/stacks/cloud/.env on the VPS if any future
# env-templated knob is added (currently none).
